145
00:06:17,375 --> 00:06:21,977
destroying? Do you even need to see that detail if you're always shooting them from 500 feet away?

146
00:06:21,977 --> 00:06:26,799
It all depends on what you're making and how you can get your animation to best

147
00:06:26,799 --> 00:06:29,299
serve how the player is going to be looking at it. Oops, I went too far.

148
00:06:33,367 --> 00:06:36,669
